  <validations type="EXPRESSION" name="DataSource_dataSourceUrlIsHttp" ownerType="DataSource" expression="value('url').startsWith('http://') || value('url').startsWith('https://')" message="Data source URL must start with http:// or https://.">
    <visualBlock blocklyBlockType="validation_expression_rule">
      <fields name="TYPE" value="DataSource"/>
      <fields name="EXPRESSION" value="value('url').startsWith('http://') || value('url').startsWith('https://')"/>
